skins.shipDescription: Independence-class light aircraft carrier C Princeton (CVL-23.)
skins.selfIntroduction: Second ship of the Independence class, Princeton, at your service. I was originally laid down as the seventh ship in the Cleveland class, Tallahassee. I fought a lot alongside Saratoga in the war, and though I was able to learn much from her, I wasn't able to make it through the Battle of Leyte Gulf... It'd be an honor to fight by her side once again.
skins.acquisition: I'm Princeton, Independence class. Tallahassee? I don't mind if you want to call me that.
skins.login: You're finally here. Did you rest well?
skins.details: Did you need something? Oh, it's fine. I wasn't doing anything special, just sorta letting my mind wander.
skins.secretaryIdle1: Sara? ...S-Saratoga is someone I admire very much. I wouldn't dare call her by her nickname.
skins.secretaryIdle2: Montpelier is a close friend of mine. It's not because we were both members of the Cleveland class, but because we both have someone we really look up to in our lives.
skins.secretaryIdle3: Feel free to give me as much work as you need. It's part of a secretary ship's duties, so don't fret it.
skins.secretaryTouch: What, do you think I'm too inexpressive? I was wondering if that's why it's like you're always trying to make me laugh.
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Have you never tried a knuckle sandwich before? How about a taste of mine... Hyah!

skins.shipDescription: Commander, are you also here to swim? ...Ah, this here? I brought it with me to the ocean to get some practice in.
skins.acquisition: Commander, are you also here to swim? ...Ah, this here? I brought it with me to the ocean to get some practice in.
skins.login: Have you done your stretches yet? You don't want to get cramps because you rushed into the ocean unprepared.
skins.details: I got this collector's edition of "Saratoga: Beautiful Summer Days" from Gridley. Looking at Saratoga enjoying the summer with everyone else makes me wish I could join her...
skins.secretaryIdle1: Hehehe. With this, I'll be able to improve my sense of balance and my physical strength at the same time. Would you like to give this a try as well?
skins.secretaryIdle2: ...It really will be a problem if my hair gets all messy from this. Um, Commander... do you think you could tie it down for me?
skins.secretaryIdle3: Independence and the others are calling for me? ...All right, I'll go.
skins.secretaryTouch: You want to get on? I-it's not that I don't want you to, but...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: W-wait a second! If you move too suddenly, it'll capsize... Wah?!
